Charlie Sumner staged a one-man pitch invasion at Reading's Madejski Stadium during their FA cup quarter final replay with Bradford City last month . 
  He did four front flips on the pitch, landing on his back each time , before being tackled by stewards . 
  The 20-year-old is facing a potential three-year ban for carrying out the stunt . 
  He said he had no regrets and that his family had 'seen the funny side'